data.title: Parti Quebecois Leader Turns His Attention To Running The Parti Quebecois
data.meta_description: MONTREAL — Pierre Karl Peladeau, who for years guided the fortunes of a sprawling media empire, will now be running a political party whose ultimate objective is Quebec independence.
